params.name: color
params.description: Changes color of stroke, uses word "hex" instead of "#", or vars, example: "var(--neutral-0)". Check for URL unsafe characters

params.name: fill
params.description: Changes fill color, uses word "hex" instead of "#", or vars, example: "var(--neutral-0)". Check for URL unsafe characters

params.name: size
params.description: Changes width and height of svg element

params.name: rotate
params.description: Adds "transform: rotate();" style at certain angle
